
<img class='center' src="neptune.gif">

<form action = "/earth" method = "post">
<input type="hidden" name="questionNumber" value="<%= @questionNumber  %>">

<% if @questionNumber == "1" %>
  <br>
  <br>
  <p>Cold War II has erupted between Russia and the United States.</p>
  <p>Nuclear bombs have been released and landed in your country, wiping out cities from the thermal blast.</p>
  <p>You suffer the effects of ionising radiation and feel ill.</p>
  <p>Do you still stay on planet Earth, or do you go to another planet in Elon Musk's SpaceX?</p>
  <br>
  <br>
<div style="text-align:center;">
  <button type="submit" value="stay" name="selection">Stay on Earth</button>
  <button type="submit" value="leave" name="selection">Leave Earth</button>
</div>
<% end %>



</form>
